{
  "stem": "24614.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I walked with burlap on my feet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the car-- was no more car because we didn't have gas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So my daddy exchanged the car for a horse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And-- but even the horse, he couldn't feed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we were very, very tired on the way home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we stopped on a farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And when we stopped on the farm, my father still had enough money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they asked them to-- if we could sleep over and to buy some food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they were giving us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we sat down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the farm was so dirty, and so-- but we sat down to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And my mother said to us, go wash your hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And this was the first time that I really felt anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I didn't know it was anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But I felt different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The woman there said, I thought the Jews are dirty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why do you have to go and wash your hands?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother looked at her and said, we wash hands before we eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she didn't make an issue out of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were nice to us until the next morning till we left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that 'the Jews are dirty' remained with me for life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came back, first of all, a lot of our friends, Jewish friends, had left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them were caught by the Germans going I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the rest of the neighbors who remained with us-- the non-Jewish neighbors didn't talk to us, just like we didn't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Jewish neighbors, we used to get together in the evenings in this home or in that home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to hear them talk-- what next?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
